Name: The Shattered Veil
Description:
For centuries, the world of Eldoria has been protected by the Veil, a barrier of mystical energy separating the material realm from the chaotic magic beyond. Now the Veil is fraying, and strange anomalies ripple across the land. The player, as the "Seeker", must uncover the extent of the decay, gather components to restore ancient Seals of power, and confront those who would exploit the chaos.
